{"id": "art-126", "label": "Art. 126", "title": "Art. 126", "slug": "art-126", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 126 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1186020537\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2292\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1186020537\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> care au calitatea\nde membri ai consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\ndirectoratului sau consiliului de supraveghere nu pot vota, în baza <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> pe care le posed&#259;, nici personal, nici\nprin mandatar, desc&#259;rcarea gestiunii lor sau o problem&#259; în care\npersoana sau <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ia</span> lor ar fi în <span\nclass=SpellE>discu&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1833354039\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2291\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1833354039\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Persoanele respective pot vota îns&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> financiar&#259; anual&#259;, dac&#259; nu se\npoate forma majoritatea prev&#259;zut&#259; de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>lege</i> sau de actul constitutiv.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}